{"tid":1590464,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"［鶳鳥］Go Go Power Ranger ，入黎幫幫手集思廣益下","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T14:47:22.000Z","uid":275380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8179b18791cea659a039e79f1f04ef612074b96e","tid":1590464,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"好想大家有首戰歌，<br />\n肥媽一曲氣勢如虹，係差啲理念上既野<br />\n<br />\nPower Ranger既OP首首歌都好正氣，<br />\n又切合神獸既意景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而鶳鳥在神話故事中確有此獸<br />\n英文為manticore <br />\n<br />\n所以今次想以 Go Go Manticore為題<br />\n做行動代號又方便<br />\n<br />\n參照：<br />\n<a href=\"https://mythology.net/mythical-creatures/manticore/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmythology.net%2Fmythical-creatures%2Fmanticore%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=6a573836\" target=\"_blank\">https://mythology.net/mythical-creatures/manticore/</a><br />\n<br />\n原曲：power rangers dino charge theme<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/power-rangers-remastered/power-rangers-dino-charge-theme-remastered\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fpower-rangers-remastered%2Fpower-rangers-dino-charge-theme-remastered&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=c13bbddd\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/power-rangers-remastered/power-rangers-dino-charge-theme-remastered</a><br />\n<br />\n原曲歌詞：<br />\nPower Rangers x4<br />\nIn a world full of strife<br />\nWe must fight to survive<br />\nTry to break the chains that divide<br />\nThere is only one chance<br />\nTo take the right stance<br />\nHold tight. Keep our power alive<br />\nGo Go Power Rangers<br />\nDon't you ever stop<br />\nGo Go Power Rangers<br />\nYou will rise up to the top<br />\nRangers Forever, Dino Charge Altogether<br />\nPower Rangers Dino Charge<br />\n<br />\n小改：<br />\nIn a world full of strife<br />\nWe must fight to survive<br />\nTry to break the chains that divide<br />\nThere is only one chance<br />\nTo take the right stance<br />\nHold tight. Keep our power alive<br />\n<br />\nGo Go Manticores<br />\nDon't you ever stop<br />\nGo Go Manticores<br />\nYou will rise up to the top<br />\nHongKongers Forever, HongKongers together<br />\n<br />\nGo Go Manticores<br />\nDon't you ever stop<br />\nGo Go Manticores<br />\nYou will rise up to the top<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">HongKongers Forever, HongKongers together</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\nAll Manticores save Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫忙俾俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd90738ea02917303c8ae696ae0c2ec61ae3fad","tid":1590464,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"be58a47071eb8b5318759ade62a5e3031c21e08c","tid":1590464,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"216bdeb2e139b843832fc5b6842b0f653f93e91f","tid":1590464,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd90738ea02917303c8ae696ae0c2ec61ae3fad","tid":1590464,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出